9/CVE-1999-0615","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Felix-sec/VulnDataExtr/blob/1f4ecda04291a8a4eb7e49189a9ee2bc026b8389/exact_keywords.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0895","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0614","title":"通用 FTP 服务运行配置问题","description":"CVE-1999-0614 候选编号已被官方拒绝使用。该条目原始描述仅指出 FTP 服务正在运行，属于系统配置管理范畴，而非独立的安全漏洞。此类配置问题更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）框架中收录，不具备传统的攻击向量、利用条件或安全影响。因此该编号不应被用于描述任何安全缺陷，也不构成对系统机密性、完整性和可用性的直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0614"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.310","remediation":"如非业务必要，建议关闭 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/proftpd 或移除对应软件包）；如必须使用，应替换为 SFTP/FTPS 等加密传输协议，并配置防火墙仅允许受信 IP 访问（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 21 -s 信任网段 -j ACCEPT），同时限制匿名登录、禁用 root 账户直接 FTP 登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0614","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/FTP%20server%20detection.plugin","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000451.txt","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-3-0__1-57240/blob/96061f959b3cf8ad81fa5d603944798cc9f3304c/atk-3.0src/plugins/Macintosh%20OS%20X%20FTP%20server%20detection.plugin"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0881","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0602","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10776,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10795}}","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理 IP 分片数据包时存在重组逻辑缺陷，无法正确还原被拆分传输的碎片包。攻击者可将恶意流量拆分为多个分片发送，使攻击载荷绕过 IDS 的特征检测与告警机制，从而在监控盲区中完成入侵行为（如端口扫描或漏洞利用投递）。该漏洞影响当时依赖分片重组能力的各类网络入侵检测产品，攻击条件为攻击者能够向目标网络注入经过分片处理的网络流量，利用方式即构造特制分片包规避检测规则。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0602"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.983","remediation":"升级所使用的网络入侵检测系统（如 Snort 升级至 1.6 及以上版本、ISS RealSecure 安装对应补丁）以修复分片重组逻辑；在 IDS  Sensor 配置中启用并正确设置 IP 分片重组（frag2/frag3）模块，合理配置碎片超时与重叠丢弃策略；在网络边界部署支持分片重组检测的防火墙，并启用防分片攻击（如限制异常小分片、丢弃重叠分片）作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0602","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0602.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/eadba179b68570c488f1a812e4ac71e19ff05906/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0880","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0601","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16293,\"outputTokens\":37,\"totalTokens\":16330}}","description":"CVE-1999-0601 是指部分网络入侵检测系统（IDS）未能正确解析和校验 TCP 握手阶段（即三次握手 SYN、SYN-ACK、ACK 数据包）中所携带的数据内容。攻击者在建立 TCP 连接时，可在握手报文中嵌入精心构造的载荷，使 IDS 解析异常或漏报，从而绕过入侵检测机制实施隐藏的恶意通信。该漏洞影响未能严格遵循 TCP 协议状态机、对握手阶段数据处理存在缺陷的 IDS 产品，利用条件为攻击者能够与目标网络建立 TCP 连接并向 IDS 镜像流量注入特制握手数据包，属于检测绕过类安全缺陷。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0601"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.863","remediation":"该漏洞源于早期网络入侵检测系统（IDS）对TCP三次握手数据包内载荷的解析缺陷，攻击者可在SYN/ACK等握手报文中夹带恶意数据以绕过检测。修复建议：升级所使用的IDS产品至厂商发布后已修复该缺陷的版本（如早期ISS RealSecure、Snort 1.3及以上等）；若暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙或路由器上启用TCP handshake normalization（如清洗握手包中的异常载荷、强制TCP状态严格校验），并开启IDS的stream重组与握手包深度检测功能以降低绕过风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0601","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0601.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000449.txt","https://github.com/adce626/VULNEX/blob/0040154d93a29bd60c2dcc4038dc3b6c26589646/lib/network-data.ts","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0601.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0879","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0600","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9122,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10805}}","description":"某网络入侵检测系统（IDS）存在安全漏洞，其根本原因在于系统在处理网络数据包时未对数据包的校验和（checksum）进行验证。攻击者可利用此缺陷构造带有错误校验和的特制数据包，这类数据包会被目标主机的协议栈丢弃，但仍能被 IDS 接收并解析，从而造成 IDS 与真实主机对流量的理解不一致。未经身份认证的远程攻击者借此可绕过入侵检测机制，使恶意流量逃避监控，或注入伪造数据干扰检测结果，进而掩盖后续攻击行为。该漏洞无需任何认证凭证，仅需向受监控网络发送数据包即可触发，影响范围覆盖所有未做校验和验证的网络入侵检测系统，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0600"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.743","remediation":"在网络入侵检测系统（IDS）的配置中启用并强制校验数据包 IP/TCP 校验和（checksum），丢弃校验和错误的伪造或篡改报文；升级到已修复该缺陷的 IDS 厂商版本（如 Snort 1.6 及以上、ISS RealSecure 最新补丁），并在边界部署状态化防火墙对异常分片与伪造流量进行过滤，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0600","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0600.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/eadba179b68570c488f1a812e4ac71e19ff05906/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0874","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0597","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16280,\"outputTokens\":37,\"totalTokens\":16317}}","description":"Windows NT 系统的账户策略存在安全配置缺陷，当远程用户的登录时段（logon hours）到期后，系统并不会强制断开其已建立的远程会话连接。受影响的系统为配置了登录时间限制的 Windows NT 服务器，远程攻击者只需在允许时段内成功登录并建立会话，即可在授权时段结束后继续保持连接，绕过登录时间限制策略，持续访问服务器资源。该漏洞源于系统未对过期会话执行强制断开机制，攻击者无需特殊权限或额外工具即可利用，属于配置与策略强制执行层面的安全问题，CVSS 评分达到 10.0 的最高危险等级。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0597"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.383","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本（含修复补丁 Q244366），或应用微软安全公告 MS99-025 对应补丁。临时缓解：在用户管理器中启用\"强制注销已过期登录时间\"策略，或部署登录脚本定时强制断开过期会话。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0597","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0597.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000446.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/76602871db1ff432e52b5609a116b2a5bc6fffe2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0872","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0596","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9111,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"Windows NT 系统的日志记录功能存在安全配置缺陷，其日志文件被设置为不适当的最大容量上限或日志保留周期，导致关键安全事件日志在达到上限后被覆盖或过早清除，无法完整记录攻击者的操作痕迹。该漏洞影响采用默认或不当日志策略的 Windows NT 系统，攻击条件为攻击者需已获得系统访问权限或利用其他漏洞进入系统，通过触发大量日志写入耗尽日志空间，使后续入侵行为难以被审计追溯，从而降低被发现和取证的概率。此问题属于安全配置不当类弱点，可通过调整日志最大大小与保留策略加以缓解。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0596"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.267","remediation":"升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2022）以消除此历史配置缺陷。对于仍需运行 Windows NT 的系统，通过事件查看器（Event Viewer）分别设置应用程序日志、系统日志和安全日志的最大大小至合理值（建议不小于 10MB），并在日志属性中配置适当的覆盖策略，选择\"按需要覆盖事件\"或\"归档日志文件后覆盖事件\"以防止日志无限增长耗尽磁盘空间。同时启用自动日志归档功能，定期将日志备份至独立存储介质，确保安全事件日志满足合规审查要求。建议在网络边界部署集中式日志管理系统（如 SIEM），将所有服务器日志统一收集存储，避免单台服务器磁盘被日志占满导致服务中断。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0596","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0596.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/76602871db1ff432e52b5609a116b2a5bc6fffe2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0870","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0593","title":"微软 Windows NT 身份验证绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Winlogon 注册表项中存在名为 ShutdownWithoutLogon 的默认配置，该配置允许尚未登录系统的用户在登录界面直接执行关机操作。此配置缺陷属于本地物理安全策略不当，影响范围覆盖默认安装的 Windows NT 操作系统。攻击条件为攻击者需具备对目标主机的物理访问权限（如可直接操作键盘、鼠标或电源按钮），利用方式是在登录屏幕未认证状态下通过界面触发关机，从而绕过正常登录审计流程，造成服务中断与本地防护绕过，可能被用于规避日志记录或配合其他物理攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0593"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.887","remediation":"在 Windows NT 注册表编辑器中定位到 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon，将 ShutdownWithoutLogon 键值从 1 修改为 0，重启后生效。此配置可禁止未登录用户通过物理访问关闭系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/59333","http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc722469.aspx","http://www.microsoft.com/technet/archive/winntas/deploy/confeat/06wntpcc.mspx?mfr=true","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1291","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0593","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0593.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86243/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0869","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0592","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 登录用户信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的登录对话框默认显示上一次成功登录的用户名，导致本地攻击者可通过物理访问目标系统获取有效账户信息。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击者利用获取的用户名可进一步实施密码猜测或暴力破解攻击，降低系统安全性。此漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，无需特殊权限即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0592"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.777","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000），微软在 SP6a 中修复了此漏洞。若无法立即升级，可通过组策略“交互式登录：不显示最后的用户名”设置为“已启用”来禁用登录框显示上次登录用户名，或修改注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon\\DontDisplayLastUserName 设为 1 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1353","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0592","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0592.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r/GHSA-6cjr-f6hr-x67r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0592.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/76602871db1ff432e52b5609a116b2a5bc6fffe2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0869.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0865","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0591","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 事件日志访问权限不当远程安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的事件日志（Event Log）配置了不恰当的访问控制权限，导致权限设置过于宽松。该漏洞影响运行 Windows NT 操作系统的服务器与工作站，攻击者只需具备本地或远程的普通用户访问权限，即可读取、篡改或清除系统安全事件日志，从而掩盖其入侵痕迹、破坏审计完整性，并可能借此获取系统配置与用户活动等敏感信息。利用方式通常为直接访问事件日志文件或调用相关 API，绕过应有的安全限制，造成日志机密性与完整性受损。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0591"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.650","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本安全更新，修复事件日志默认权限配置不当问题。如无法安装补丁，通过 regedt32 将注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\EventLog 的权限限制为仅 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 完全控制，并确保 %SystemRoot%\\System32\\config\\*.evt 文件权限仅允许 Administrators 组读写。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0591.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j448-c6cm-wxq3/GHSA-j448-c6cm-wxq3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86255/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml"}]